Core Capabilities
- Activates Microsoft products with KMS emulation for seamless software licensing.
- Portable application requires no installation, running directly from USB drives.
- Supports Windows, Office, and other Microsoft software activation processes.
- Features a user-friendly interface for quick access to all tools.
- Provides detailed logs for monitoring activation and performance metrics.

